        <i class="fa fa-pencil fa-3x myHeader"></i>
        <h2 class="myHeader">Apply</h2>
        <p>
            We're doing our best to simply what is
            a very comprehensive process into a series of intuitive steps. However, some things are just too complex to be simple,
            which is why some applications recommend retaining the use of an attorney or licensed professional.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a class="btn btn-default myHeader" href="@Url.Action("About")">Learn more &raquo;</a>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <i class="fa fa-share-alt fa-3x myHeader"></i>
        <h2 class="myHeader">Share</h2>
        <p>
            Apply for Subdivision and Mapping applications online through this website. You can invite others to edit your application.
            Save your application and return to it at any time. Upload file attachments, and sign documents all in this one place.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a class="btn btn-default myHeader" href="@Url.Action("About")">Learn more &raquo;</a>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <i class="fa fa-eye fa-3x myHeader"></i>
        <h2 class="myHeader">Track</h2>
        <p>Track the status of any submitted project through our Subdivision Tracking System. Applications only appear after an electronic application is submitted here, the applicant has paid the invoice in full, and has been reviewed by our staff</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default myHeader" href="https://bsm.sfdpw.org/subdivision/tracking/">Learn more &raquo;</a> </p>
